---
title: Pan-Seared Shrimp and Zesty Garlic Sauce with Potato Coins and Citrus Salad
description: Simple shrimp is brought to life with a zesty garlic sauce! Paired with a citrus salad and crunchy sunflower seeds, this is a perfect, bright plate for any meal.

